ATA History / Versions
	ATA-1 (IDE)
		Supported 2 drives
		Utilized CHS (Cylinder, Head, Sector)
		Supports drives up to 504 MB
	ATA-2 (EIDE/ATAPI) 
		Utilized LBA 
		Supports drives up to 8.4 GB
		Supported optical drives
		Supported 4 drives

